  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>For breakfast enjoy a buffet with hot options and delicious pancakes; they have a fantastic pancake maker! In the evening the hotel serves a four-course dinner with various choices, the food will give you a taste of Italy and the Val D'Aosta.</p>
<p>Packed lunches are available for €4 per person (payable locally). These include a sandwich, fruit and water and can be ordered at reception.</p>
<p>You'll also receive a 10% discount at La Mandria, a local mountain restaurant where you can enjoy lunch. La Mandria can be booked locally at the hotel.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
