  <description><![CDATA[<p>You’ll feel like you’re in your own home when staying at the Hotel de Champoluc. The staff are welcoming and the lounge has board games and books dotted around. It’s in the centre of Champoluc, right next door to the Crest gondola so perfect for heading into the mountains.</p>
<h2>Fantastic location in central Champoluc</h2>
<p>The Hotel is situated right at the foot of Monte Rosa and next door to the Crest gondola. Why not jump on the gondola and head into the mountains to discover some great walking trails or wander through the town. From the hotel you have easy access to local amenities, restaurants and shops. </p>
<h2>Hearty Meals</h2>
<p>Breakfast is always a hit at the Hotel de Champoluc with plenty of choices available from the buffet as well as hot options. We particularly love the pancake making machine! You'll experience some lovely Italian food, with some authentic, local dishes from the Aosta Valley to give you a real feel for the area.</p>
<p><strong>Transfer time:</strong> approx. 2 hours by coach from Milan airport. </p>]]></description>
